{"ts": "2026-06-08T13:38:21.067549+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14cdb62b2e100f4ebf75f88cf5c58669437208e3)", "id": "lc_05165b3d-5d5e-4a42-bdff-01adedede968"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# vue3-vite-starter-template\n\nA single page app [Vite](https://vitejs.dev) starter template, created to easily bootstrap Vue.js 3 apps.\n\n**Features**\n\n- Vitest for unit testing\n- Pinia for state management\n- Vue Router 4 for client-side routing\n- Bootstrap 5.3 for layout and styling\n- SCSS variables inside Vue components\n- Purgecss for eliminating unused CSS\n- Basic multiple layouts feature\n- ESLint config based on `eslint:recommended` with sensible defaults :relaxed:\n- [Prettier](https://prettier.io/) for code formatting\n- Automated release workflow with [semantic-release](https://github.com/semantic-release/semantic-release)\n\n## Project setup\n\n```\npnpm install\n```\n\n### Compiles and hot-reloads for development\n\n```\npnpm run dev\n```\n\n### Compiles and minifies for production\n\n```\npnpm run build\n```\n\n## Run your unit tests\n\n```\npnpm run test:unit\n```\n\n### Lints files\n\n```\npnpm run lint\n```\n\n### Lints and fixes files\n\n```\nnpm run lint-fix\n```\n\n### Customize configuration\n\nSee [Configuration Reference](https://vitejs.dev/guide/).\n", "id": "lc_5ba37d76-6dba-4a2a-b399-5a71d0e4d599"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "523f07f0-da6b-4ad0-aec5-7dd0ec69ffc6", "tool_call_id": "call_01_CFBwKOxexAUZ8jwwMsfI0160", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-08T13:38:21.194790+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14e35346190d0ff04ea56d634a34dbac593ed1c9)", "id": "lc_2f514589-a5dd-46b5-9074-f764dc4fb36e"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"name\": \"vue3-vite-starter-template\",\n  \"description\": \"Vue.js 3 Vite starter template with Pinia, Vue Router, Bootstrap and more.\",\n  \"version\": \"0.0.0-semantic-release\",\n  \"license\": \"MIT\",\n  \"repository\": \"https://github.com/kouts/vue3-vite-starter-template\",\n  \"packageManager\": \"pnpm@10.20.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"preinstall\": \"npx only-allow pnpm\",\n    \"dev\": \"vite\",\n    \"build\": \"vite build\",\n    \"preview\": \"vite preview\",\n    \"build-preview\": \"vite build && vite preview\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint \\\"**/*.{vue,ts,js}\\\"\",\n    \"lint-fix\": \"eslint --fix \\\"**/*.{vue,ts,js}\\\"\",\n    \"test:unit\": \"vitest\",\n    \"test:unit-coverage\": \"vitest run --coverage\",\n    \"prepare\": \"husky\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"bootstrap\": \"^5.3.8\",\n    \"jsdom\": \"^27.1.0\",\n    \"pinia\": \"^3.0.3\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^4.0.6\",\n    \"vue\": \"^3.5.22\",\n    \"vue-router\": \"^4.6.3\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@commitlint/cli\": \"^20.1.0\",\n    \"@commitlint/config-conventional\": \"^20.0.0\",\n    \"@fullhuman/postcss-purgecss\": \"^7.0.2\",\n    \"@fullhuman/vue-cli-plugin-purgecss\": \"^7.0.2\",\n    \"@kouts/eslint-config\": \"^3.0.9\",\n    \"@vitejs/plugin-vue\": \"^6.0.1\",\n    \"@vue/compiler-sfc\": \"^3.5.22\",\n    \"@vue/test-utils\": \"^2.4.6\",\n    \"autoprefixer\": \"^10.4.21\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^9.39.0\",\n    \"husky\": \"^9.1.7\",\n    \"lint-staged\": \"^16.2.6\",\n    \"prettier\": \"^3.6.2\",\n    \"sass\": \"^1.93.3\",\n    \"vite\": \"^7.1.12\",\n    \"vite-plugin-html\": \"^3.2.2\"\n  }\n}", "id": "lc_58b18bf6-1997-479b-bb19-ae2cd67d0417"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "15866e80-d9a8-41dc-a62d-fda0253bcb02", "tool_call_id": "call_00_67RcEGl1qawvGgBNaADN2640", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-08T13:38:27.828332+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Now I have a clear picture of the project. Here's a summary of the setup and day-to-day development commands:\n\n---\n\n## Repository: `vue3-vite-starter-template`\n\nA Vue.js 3 Vite starter template with Pinia, Vue Router, Bootstrap, Vitest, ESLint, and more.\n\n### Setup (first-time)\n\n```bash\npnpm install\n```\n\n> **Note:** The project enforces `pnpm` via a `preinstall` script (`npx only-allow pnpm`). Do not use `npm` or `yarn`.\n\n### Day-to-day development commands\n\n| Command | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `pnpm run dev` | Start the Vite development server with hot-reload |\n| `pnpm run build` | Compile and minify for production |\n| `pnpm run preview` | Preview the production build locally |\n| `pnpm run build-preview` | Build and then preview |\n| `pnpm run test:unit` | Run unit tests (Vitest) |\n| `pnpm run test:unit-coverage` | Run unit tests with coverage report |\n| `pnpm run lint` | Lint all `.vue`, `.ts`, `.js` files with ESLint |\n| `pnpm run lint-fix` | Lint and automatically fix fixable issues |\n\n### Additional tooling\n\n- **Prettier** – code formatting (config: `prettier.config.js`)\n- **Husky** + **commitlint** + **lint-staged** – Git hooks for commit message linting and pre-commit linting\n- **Semantic-release** – automated release workflow (config: `release.config.js`)\n- **PurgeCSS** – removes unused CSS in production builds\n\n---\n\nAll scripts are defined in `package.json` under the `\"scripts\"` key and follow the standard Vite/Vue.js conventions.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 653, "prompt_tokens": 4314, "total_tokens": 4967, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 255, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 3328}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 3328, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 986}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-flash", "system_fingerprint": "fp_8b330d02d0_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "32c70e4d-5af6-4939-9229-741c7c27b69b", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea774-a98c-7620-bff4-88a116c1171b-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 4314, "output_tokens": 653, "total_tokens": 4967, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 3328}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 255}}}}]}}}
